inlineContent.text: A contact object that represents the new shipping address. To maintain privacy, the shipping information is anonymized. For example, in the United States it only includes the city, state, and zip code. This information provides enough detail to calculate shipping costs, without revealing sensitive information until the user actually approves the purchase.
The completion handler to call with the updated payment summary items and shipping methods.
